    {
      "id": "BzviHG6oi3YulXWE9E52T",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 228.81105041503906,
      "y": 242.76129150390625,
      "width": 541.07958984375,
      "height": 1450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bb1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2084181108,
      "version": 1003,
      "versionNonce": 635139444,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783235852555,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Questions:\n\nq. system like google maps?\nyes\n\nq. imp features?\n- Business can add/ update/delete theri details\nany verification during add? yes\n- Customers can search for businesses based on types \nliek petrol pumps, grocery, restaurants etc\n\nq. delay in business being added and apprear in search \nresults?\n- Yes, delay is expected\n\nq. scale\n100m businesses over the world\n1b customers\n20% DAU\n\nq. business location static?\nyes\n\nq. radius of search\nconfigurable, 1 km, 5 km , 20 km default\n\nq. search radius constant or expanding?\nconstant\n\nFunctional req:\n- Business can add/ update/delete theri details\n- Customers can search for businesses based on types \nliek petrol pumps, grocery, restaurants etc\n\nNFR:\nAvailability : 99.9\nScalable\nReliable\nLow latency\n\nBack of teh envelope calc:\n100 m businesses\n200 m customer * 5 search queries a day\n1 b queries a day\n\n1 * 10^9 / 10^5 = 10000 rps\n\nWrites:\nbusiness updates : 5% businesses upadtes a day\n5 * 10^6 / 10^5 = 50 writes per second\n\nStorage:\nbusiness 100m * 1kb\n= 100 * 10^6 kb\n= 100 gb\n\nsearch\ntodo",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Questions:\n\nq. system like google maps?\nyes\n\nq. imp features?\n- Business can add/ update/delete theri details\nany verification during add? yes\n- Customers can search for businesses based on types \nliek petrol pumps, grocery, restaurants etc\n\nq. delay in business being added and apprear in search \nresults?\n- Yes, delay is expected\n\nq. scale\n100m businesses over the world\n1b customers\n20% DAU\n\nq. business location static?\nyes\n\nq. radius of search\nconfigurable, 1 km, 5 km , 20 km default\n\nq. search radius constant or expanding?\nconstant\n\nFunctional req:\n- Business can add/ update/delete theri details\n- Customers can search for businesses based on types \nliek petrol pumps, grocery, restaurants etc\n\nNFR:\nAvailability : 99.9\nScalable\nReliable\nLow latency\n\nBack of teh envelope calc:\n100 m businesses\n200 m customer * 5 search queries a day\n1 b queries a day\n\n1 * 10^9 / 10^5 = 10000 rps\n\nWrites:\nbusiness updates : 5% businesses upadtes a day\n5 * 10^6 / 10^5 = 50 writes per second\n\nStorage:\nbusiness 100m * 1kb\n= 100 * 10^6 kb\n= 100 gb\n\nsearch\ntodo",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
