      "seed": 1405878900,
      "version": 377,
      "versionNonce": 1451478220,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783234124952,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Flow :\n1. Business adds/ upadtes/ deletes their business\n2. API gateway\n    Auth\n    Routing\n    Logging\n    Rate limiting\n3. Business service : service for business owners to\nadd/uodate/delete business\n4. DB : Read heavy\n    SQL : Postgres\n    NoSQL\n\n1. Customer searches for business based on type in n radius\n2. Search service gets the data",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Flow :\n1. Business adds/ upadtes/ deletes their business\n2. API gateway\n    Auth\n    Routing\n    Logging\n    Rate limiting\n3. Business service : service for business owners to\nadd/uodate/delete business\n4. DB : Read heavy\n    SQL : Postgres\n    NoSQL\n\n1. Customer searches for business based on type in n radius\n2. Search service gets the data",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "BDKILynROQVw_P7mCbiwe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2291.844207763672,
      "y": 215.50372314453125,
      "width": 568.69970703125,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bbS",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2088301300,
      "version": 461,
      "versionNonce": 486846324,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783234613162,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem:\nIndex on geolocation\n\nSQL : postgress\nWHERE lat >= ? and lat <= ? and long <= ? and long >= ?\n\nwe will get all lat and long in that range.\nwe need to convert 2d into 1d to be converted into index\n\nSolution:\n1. GeoHash\n2. Quadtree\n3. Google S2 ( based on quadtree)\n\n1. GeoHash\nCreate hash of geolocation\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem:\nIndex on geolocation\n\nSQL : postgress\nWHERE lat >= ? and lat <= ? and long <= ? and long >= ?\n\nwe will get all lat and long in that range.\nwe need to convert 2d into 1d to be converted into index\n\nSolution:\n1. GeoHash\n2. Quadtree\n3. Google S2 ( based on quadtree)\n\n1. GeoHash\nCreate hash of geolocation\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "DkZEbiF0KB4ypfHWd9tqO",
      "type": "text",
