      "updated": 1783236033307,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Availability: 99.9 to 99.99\nEKS\nAurora\nMulti region and Az deployemnt \n\nDB :\nPostgress : \n1. Partition by region and business id\n2. Replication\n\nScale quad tree :\nadd in memory and repliate\n\nWhen to invalidate tree :\nDaily and build new tree\n\nDo blue green like real time updates\n\nWe can filter results by type and openng time on servicde",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Availability: 99.9 to 99.99\nEKS\nAurora\nMulti region and Az deployemnt \n\nDB :\nPostgress : \n1. Partition by region and business id\n2. Replication\n\nScale quad tree :\nadd in memory and repliate\n\nWhen to invalidate tree :\nDaily and build new tree\n\nDo blue green like real time updates\n\nWe can filter results by type and openng time on servicde",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
